        "description": "Townsmen VR uses the exciting possibilities of virtual reality to further enhance the classic city-building game with entirely new gameplay experiences and interactive mechanics. The game combines elements of a God-game simulation and a classic building game with the interactive possibilities of VR controls. Whether from a bird's eye view or zoomed-in close, you will always experience the action from the right perspective.\n\nStart with a small settlement and expand your might over a world of 13 different islands and archipelagos. Filled to the brim with exciting features, gizmos, and things to lay your virtual hands on. Build more than 20 unique buildings and upgrade them. Immerse yourself in a thrilling story with many exciting quests that will provide you with hours of fun!\n\nMost of the islands you visit during the campaign can be unlocked for unrestricted play in the sandbox mode – the various settings offer you enough freedom for your personal gaming experience!\n\n● A fully-voiced campaign and story arching over 13 islands.\n● Assign jobs and tasks to your villagers to build your supply chains and economy.\n● Unlock more than 20 unique buildings and place them freely within your village to optimize transport routes. Apply upgrades to make them better!\n● Recruit brave soldiers, and build catapults, bows, and crossbows to protect your island from raiding henchmen.",
